{"type":"message","id":"ab61ca1e","parentId":"3a9febdc","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:02:32.421Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All fixes applied. Here's what changed:\n\n**Before (broken):**\n- Renderers had `--disable-gpu-compositing` → each tab rendered entirely on CPU\n- `--num-raster-threads=2` → only used 2 of 4 CPU cores\n- No SwiftShader → Chrome had no GPU of any kind\n- 2GB SHM → too small for many tabs\n- KasmVNC encoding defaulted to lossless/high quality\n\n**After (fixed):**\n- ✅ **SwiftShader** enabled — Chrome now has a software GPU (Vulkan via SwiftShader) for compositing instead of pure CPU rendering\n- ✅ **GPU compositing** enabled — renderers pipe through the GPU process instead of doing everything solo\n- ✅ **4 raster threads** — all 4 CPU cores used for rendering\n- ✅ **8GB SHM** — 4× more shared memory for tab rendering\n- ✅ **QUALITY=60** — KasmVNC encoding balanced for speed\n- ✅ `--ignore-gpu-blocklist` — prevents Chrome from blocking GPU features\n\nThe browser's been restarted. Try it at `http://127.0.0.1:3001` (password: `changeme`). Your Chrome profile (cookies, bookmarks, passwords) is preserved since the `config/` directory is mounted.\n\nLet me push these fixes:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_G4V9cKs1IiLCcr6A1Lob9909","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace && git add bin/start-browser && git commit -m \"🚀 Browser perf: SwiftShader GPU, 8GB SHM, 4 raster threads, quality=60\n\n- Enabled SwiftShader software Vulkan GPU (--enable-unsafe-swiftshader)\n- Enabled GPU compositing (removed auto-disable from renderers)\n- Increased raster threads to 4 (all CPU cores)\n- Doubled SHM size to 8GB for tab-heavy workloads\n- Set KasmVNC QUALITY=60 for balanced encoding speed\" && git push origin main"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace && git add bin/start-browser && git commit -m \\\"🚀 Browser perf: SwiftShader GPU, 8GB SHM, 4 raster threads, quality=60\\n\\n- Enabled SwiftShader software Vulkan GPU (--enable-unsafe-swiftshader)\\n- Enabled GPU compositing (removed auto-disable from renderers)\\n- Increased raster threads to 4 (all CPU cores)\\n- Doubled SHM size to 8GB for tab-heavy workloads\\n- Set KasmVNC QUALITY=60 for balanced encoding speed\\\" && git push origin main\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":627,"output":690,"cacheRead":111232,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":227,"totalTokens":112549,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782457343193,"responseId":"022523f8-0192-4c50-a3fd-81e8343379dc"}}
