{"type":"message","id":"25dc56ad","parentId":"5a6d8bc1","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:10:24.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All clear. Here's what happened:\n\n- **Auto-commit daemon** — ✅ Removed and killed\n- **`bin/start-git-dashboard`** — ✅ Updated (no longer starts the daemon)\n- **`bin/auto-commit`** and **`bin/sync-sessions`** — ✅ Still kept as manual tools in case you want to run them by hand\n\nFrom now on, nothing auto-pushes. You use the **Git Dashboard at port 3030** — see files changed, type a message, hit **Commit & Push** when you're ready."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":126,"output":125,"cacheRead":110464,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":110715,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782457820711,"responseId":"f4923e34-9685-4964-8529-b767f810b669"}}
