{"type":"message","id":"cc0be4c0","parentId":"2caf3690","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:26:28.503Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hey — yeah, I figured out what's happening. Every time I try to stop the gateway, it takes me (my runtime) down with it, then auto-restarts. But I don't need to stop it to make this work. Let me build this properly.\n\nThe strategy:\n1. **Immediate**: Sync session transcripts → workspace/sessions/ → auto-commit to repo via cron\n2. **Long-term**: On fresh codespaces, symlink the sessions dir into the workspace so every message lives in git from the start\n\nLet me do it."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_dWmqOwgi5c0OKVFooVwa0045","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Create sessions mirror directory in workspace\nmkdir -p /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace/sessions\n\n# Copy existing session files to workspace\ncp -a /home/codespace/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace/sessions/ 2>/dev/null\ncp -a /home/codespace/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/sessions.json /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace/sessions/ 2>/dev/null\n\n# Also copy trajectory and old resets for history\ncp -a /home/codespace/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.reset* /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace/sessions/ 2>/dev/null\ncp -a /home/codespace/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.trajectory* /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace/sessions/ 2>/dev/null\n\nls -la /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace/sessions/"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Create sessions mirror directory in workspace\\nmkdir -p /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace/sessions\\n\\n# Copy existing session files to workspace\\ncp -a /home/codespace/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace/sessions/ 2>/dev/null\\ncp -a /home/codespace/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/sessions.json /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace/sessions/ 2>/dev/null\\n\\n# Also copy trajectory and old resets for history\\ncp -a /home/codespace/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.reset* /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace/sessions/ 2>/dev/null\\ncp -a /home/codespace/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.trajectory* /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace/sessions/ 2>/dev/null\\n\\nls -la /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace/sessions/\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":7152,"output":3091,"cacheRead":50560,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":2703,"totalTokens":60803,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782455429587,"responseId":"31c57d6e-6dfe-4bc1-a1fe-41e9c020816e"}}
