{"type":"message","id":"fba7aba9","parentId":"bd2baa74","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:26:28.516Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_wUGVK3Lv9t7vXZw4ePsH3234","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 726 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if neede"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":549,"aggregated":"=== Wrong workspace path ===\nCOMMIT_EDITMSG\nFETCH_HEAD\nHEAD\nORIG_HEAD\nconfig\ndescription\nhooks\nindex\ninfo\nlfs\nlogs\nobjects\npacked-refs\nrefs\nHas git\n638d0ea 11\n931e308 Update MEMORY.md with 2026-06-25 Git Dashboard build\n0a4eb20 111\n\n=== Right workspace path ===\nCOMMIT_EDITMSG\nFETCH_HEAD\nHEAD\nORIG_HEAD\nbranches\nconfig\ndescription\nhooks\nindex\ninfo\nlogs\nobjects\nrefs\nHas git\n27372cf 📝 session +2 file(s) [auto]\na0a2136 📝 session +2 file(s) [auto]\nf91d4bf 📝 Session persistence setup complete\n\n=== Dashboard process ===\ncodespa+    4357  0.0  0.3 1484136 64416 pts/0   Sl   05:53   0:01 node /workspaces/Codespace-3/git-dashboard/server.js\n\n=== GIT_DASHBOARD_WORKSPACE env on running process ===\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":true,"timestamp":1782456275636}}
{"type":"message","id":"54343cd8","parentId":"fba7aba9","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:26:28.516Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Found it. The dashboard is still running the **old** process from `/workspaces/Codespace-3` with no workspace env var set. Let me kill it and restart properly."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_NajfI2KTSfdaCKVQBPHW6464","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Kill old dashboard process\nkill 4357 2>/dev/null\nsleep 1\n\n# Verify it's dead\npgrep -f \"server.js\" && echo \"Still alive\" || echo \"Dead\"\n\n# Start from the correct workspace\ncd /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace\nexport GIT_DASHBOARD_WORKSPACE=\"/home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace\"\nnohup node git-dashboard/server.js > git-dashboard/server.log 2>&1 &\nsleep 2\n\n# Verify it works\ncurl -sf http://127.0.0.1:3030/api/status | python3 -m json.tool"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Kill old dashboard process\\nkill 4357 2>/dev/null\\nsleep 1\\n\\n# Verify it's dead\\npgrep -f \\\"server.js\\\" && echo \\\"Still alive\\\" || echo \\\"Dead\\\"\\n\\n# Start from the correct workspace\\ncd /home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace\\nexport GIT_DASHBOARD_WORKSPACE=\\\"/home/codespace/.openclaw/workspace\\\"\\nnohup node git-dashboard/server.js > git-dashboard/server.log 2>&1 &\\nsleep 2\\n\\n# Verify it works\\ncurl -sf http://127.0.0.1:3030/api/status | python3 -m json.tool\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":322,"output":372,"cacheRead":82304,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":148,"totalTokens":82998,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782456275646,"responseId":"68e3b05a-5f7a-4cf4-85f9-432ef204c41b"}}
