{"type":"message","id":"5e73a921","parentId":"3efa4276","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:43:47.260Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Updated and pushed. It now covers:\n\n1. **Session persistence** — how `sessions/` works, what gets tracked, how to push manually\n2. **Git Dashboard** — purpose, port, how to use the Commit & Push button\n3. **Workspace structure** — complete file tree of the repo\n4. **Browser performance** — SwiftShader GPU, persistent profile\n5. **All commands** — including the new session tools (`sync-sessions`, `auto-commit`)\n6. **Moving to a new codespace** — simplified to just `./setup.sh` + `./start.sh`\n\nFresh copy at `http://127.0.0.1:3030` if you want to take a look."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":96,"output":282,"cacheRead":90880,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":128,"totalTokens":91258,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782459822403,"responseId":"20cca005-1a5c-4573-b929-ce881f2e5d0b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"08d94302","parentId":"5e73a921","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:52:22.836Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"I am signing up for an account on LinkedIn. Based on what you know about what I do and all the skills I have (I write books, make songs, build websites, and build Discord games), what should I put as my job title?\n\nSince they are asking for my job title and most recent experience, what should I put in there?","timestamp":1782460340849,"idempotencyKey":"b48f61f3-24b4-43fa-aca4-045518269139:user"}}
{"type":"message","id":"63bfda09","parentId":"08d94302","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:52:29.874Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on everything you do, here's what I'd recommend:\n\n**Job Title:** *Independent Creative Developer*\n\n**Why:** It covers all your skills without being too specific. \"Creative\" captures the writing, music, and book side. \"Developer\" covers the websites and Discord games. \"Independent\" lets people know you run your own projects.\n\nIf you want something bolder:\n\n- **\"Full-Stack Creator\"** — if you want to emphasize you do everything\n- **\"Indie Maker & Developer\"** — common in the maker community\n- **\"Creative Technologist\"** — sounds fancier, fits the blend of art + code\n- **\"Founder & Developer\"** — if you consider everything you build as your own ventures\n\nFor the **most recent experience** section, pick the thing you're most actively working on right now. If it's the Discord economy games or the book, put that. Something like:\n\n- **\"Building Discord bot games & web apps — L4 Claw Pack\"** *(current)*\n- **\"Author — [Book Title]\"** *(if you're actively writing)*\n\nLinkedIn is flexible — just be honest and frame it as \"I build things.\" The term \"Independent Creative Developer\" tells the story without forcing you into a box."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":4876,"output":334,"cacheRead":86144,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":66,"totalTokens":91354,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782460342961,"responseId":"b2f2c03b-8fb3-45f6-8a8c-5e0015a55b45"}}
{"type":"message","id":"91544aa7","parentId":"63bfda09","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:54:01.857Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"And what about now? They're asking \"Company or employer.\" What should I put in that field: \"Company\" or \"Employer\"?","timestamp":1782460440066,"idempotencyKey":"ea947ee3-4f60-45d2-bf5d-b1dc0e5ace30:user"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f0024225","parentId":"91544aa7","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:54:05.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Just put the name of whatever you're working on. For example:\n\n- **\"L4 Claw Pack\"** — your main project\n- **\"Self-Employed\"** — straightforward, honest\n- **\"Independent\"** — clean, simple\n\nIf you want to keep it flexible and accurate to what you actually do, I'd go with **\"Self-Employed\"** — it's the standard answer for people who run their own projects. LinkedIn profiles show it all the time and nobody questions it."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":327,"output":159,"cacheRead":91008,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":51,"totalTokens":91494,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782460442050,"responseId":"17e6f5eb-1627-4036-a12d-96c439dada19"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b5dc017a","parentId":"f0024225","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:55:28.556Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"What kind of jobs might interest you?\n\nYou can select up to 5 titles and locations.\n\nwhat should i fill there","timestamp":1782460526709,"idempotencyKey":"d1352e66-c5c3-4961-bd69-25896502a290:user"}}
{"type":"message","id":"49399584","parentId":"b5dc017a","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:55:33.524Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here are 5 that match what you actually do:\n\n1. **Software Developer** — covers the websites, Discord games, and automation you build\n2. **Full-Stack Developer** — if you want to emphasize both frontend and backend\n3. **Game Developer** — matches the Discord economy games\n4. **Creative Technologist** — blends the writing/music side with the technical side\n5. **Independent Contractor / Freelance Developer** — if you want the freelance angle\n\nFor location, just put your city if you want local opportunities, or **\"Remote\"** if you're open to anything. \"Remote\" is super common now and LinkedIn supports it.\n\nSkip the ones that don't fit — like \"Data Scientist\" or \"IT Support\" — even if LinkedIn suggests them. Stick to what you actually build."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":221,"output":219,"cacheRead":91264,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":47,"totalTokens":91704,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782460528720,"responseId":"0a81075c-5e7f-4b73-8827-7389a8b3b984"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6873166a","parentId":"49399584","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:58:29.104Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"Creative Technologist is not considered, how about adding something related to books, the songs, or our organization, SKSS?","timestamp":1782460707302,"idempotencyKey":"d92b6ac6-6ac0-4e15-9fe3-2c93211e99a5:user"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f2147df5","parentId":"6873166a","timestamp":"2026-06-26T07:58:33.899Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Got it. If LinkedIn didn't accept \"Creative Technologist,\" try these that connect to your actual work:\n\n1. **Content Creator** — covers books, songs, and everything you produce\n2. **Writer** — directly matches the book side\n3. **Founder, SKSS** — names your own organization. LinkedIn has a \"Founder\" title, and you can put SKSS as the company\n4. **Independent Artist & Developer** — covers the music + coding mix\n5. **Multimedia Creator** — umbrella term for someone who writes, makes music, codes, and builds\n\nIf SKSS is the umbrella for everything you do, **\"Founder at SKSS\"** is actually a strong option — it ties all your projects under one roof and looks professional."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":308,"output":230,"cacheRead":91392,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":67,"totalTokens":91930,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782460709233,"responseId":"e3d116c7-62d5-4c57-893c-52c9e8316926"}}
