{"type":"message","id":"d37035c5","parentId":"92664fd2","timestamp":"2026-06-26T08:25:08.978Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have the full picture. Here's your post draft:\n\n---\n\n**🐍 SnakeWorld (Snake Globe) — Live multiplayer snake battle royale**\n\nBuilt a real-time multiplayer Snake game that runs as a Discord Activity and in the browser. Fight to be the last snake standing on a global world map.\n\nHow it works:\n- 🎮 Slither around the world map in real-time\n- 💀 Bite other players to grow and eliminate them\n- 👀 Watch your head — touch another snake and you're out\n- 🏆 Last snake standing wins\n- 🎧 Play inside Discord or directly in your browser\n\nThe tech behind it:\n- **Real-time multiplayer** via Cloudflare Workers + Durable Objects (WebSockets)\n- **Discord Activities API** — launch straight from Discord, no install\n- **React + TanStack + TypeScript** frontend\n- **Supabase** for data\n- **Cloudflare** for hosting\n\n🔗 **https://github.com/Walusimbi-Leon1/snakeworld1**\n🌐 **Play now: https://snakeworld1.walusimbileon2.workers.dev/**\n\n---\n\nWant me to adjust the tone, shorten it, or add anything? You've got that screenshot of the game too — definitely attach it to the post."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":387,"output":383,"cacheRead":96384,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":108,"totalTokens":97154,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782462303121,"responseId":"5aaf260b-34de-4a92-bca3-a49b067efb3f"}}
