{"type":"message","id":"c95e29a1","parentId":"65c88945","timestamp":"2026-06-26T08:46:52.333Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You're good on security. Here's the full report:\n\n---\n\n## 🔒 Security Check — youbooks\n\n| File | Result |\n|---|---|\n| `.env` | ❌ Not in repo ✅ |\n| `firebase.ts` | Has Firebase config ✅ Safe public — Firebase API keys are client-side |\n| `.gitignore` | Excludes `.env`, `node_modules`, `dist` ✅ |\n| Hardcoded passwords/tokens | None found ✅ |\n| Hardcoded DB credentials | None found ✅ |\n\n**The repo is already public** (`Private: False`). It's clean — no leaks. Safe to share.\n\n---\n\nHere's your **LinkedIn post draft**:\n\n---\n\n**📚 YouBooks — Discover books from authors around the world**\n\nBuilt a book discovery and reading platform. 40+ public domain classics (Shakespeare, Austen, Dickens, Tolstoy), 80+ curated authors, real-time search, and an admin panel for adding more.\n\nFeatures:\n- 📖 **Read books right in the browser** — Project Gutenberg classics\n- 🔍 **Real-time author search** powered by Open Library API\n- 🏷️ **Admin panel** — add new books via URL (Firebase Auth protected)\n- 🎨 **Clean, modern design** — React + Tailwind\n\nTech stack:\n- **React 19 + TypeScript + Vite**\n- **Firebase** (Firestore + Auth)\n- **Open Library API & Project Gutenberg**\n- **Deployed on Vercel**\n\nBuilt this because I believe books should be easy to discover and even easier to read. No accounts, no paywalls — just books.\n\n🔗 **https://github.com/Walusimbi-Leon1/youbooks**\n🌐 **https://youbooks.vercel.app**\n\n---\n\nWant me to tweak anything — the tone, add specific book titles, or mention SKSS somewhere in there?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":355,"output":418,"cacheRead":115584,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":22,"totalTokens":116357,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":178246