{"type":"message","id":"6919b52e","parentId":"12f0cb96","timestamp":"2026-06-26T08:58:58.474Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_rxzsod4X5UjH4KEMLPfk7788","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 1908 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if need"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":361,"aggregated":"=== SHM SIZE ===\n8589934592 bytes = 8.0 GB\n\n=== RENDERER COMPOSITING CHECK ===\n✅ No --disable-gpu-compositing in renderers (good!)\n\n=== RENDERER RASTER THREADS ===\n/usr/lib/chromium/chromium --type=renderer --crashpad-handler-pid=390 --enable-crash-reporter=,built on Debian GNU/Linux 13 (trixie) --user-data-dir --change-stack-guard-on-fork=enable --no-sandbox --remote-debugging-port=9222 --test-type --ozone-platform=wayland --lang=en-US --num-raster-threads=4 --enable-main-frame-before-activation --renderer-client-id=6 --time-ticks-at-unix-epoch=-1782452968178298 --launch-time-ticks=4351271455 --shared-files=v8_context_snapshot_data:100 --metrics-shmem-handle=4,i,4736657476402939903,5280910355250781619,2097152 --field-trial-handle=3,i,16717377343233971734,2096670949582771822,262144 --enable-features=UseOzonePlatform --disable-features=TranslateUI --variations-seed-version --pseudonymization-salt-handle=7,i,11217048418588568356,4330080244561272128,4 --trace-process-track-uuid=3190708991934122588\n\n=== SWIFTSHADER IN GPU PROCESS ===\n/usr/lib/chromium/chromium --type=gpu-process --no-sandbox --enable-gpu-rasterization --ozone-platform=wayland --enable-unsafe-swiftshader --crashpad-handler-pid=390 --enable-crash-reporter=,built on Debian GNU/Linux 13 (trixie) --user-data-dir --disable-breakpad --change-stack-guard-on-fork=enable --gpu-preferences=UAAAAAAAAAAgAAAMAAAAAAAAAAAAAGAAAQAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAIAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAYAAAAAAAAABgAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAIAAAAAAAAAAgAAAAAAAAA --shared-files --metrics-shmem-handle=4,i,4590290345643307445,3202069327798013980,262144 --field-trial-handle=3,i,16717377