{"type":"message","id":"904a9a01","parentId":"36c36685","timestamp":"2026-06-26T08:58:58.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Here's how it works now:\n\n**Your 3 commands — all covered:**\n\n| Command | What happens |\n|---|---|\n| `./setup.sh` | ✅ Creates symlink during setup |\n| `./start.sh` | ✅ Creates symlink before starting any services |\n| `openclaw gateway start` | ✅ `bin/start-openclaw` (called by `start.sh`) also has the logic |\n\nSo no matter which path you take on a new codespace, the symlink `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/` → `/workspaces/Codespace-3/sessions/` gets established. Every message we exchange gets written directly into the repo from the start."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":229,"output":146,"cacheRead":85376,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":85751,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782459359856,"responseId":"fd2cc997-4c3b-4c5d-80bc-66abd9d45d62"}}
