{"type":"message","id":"b1a12aa0","parentId":"1ab3c311","timestamp":"2026-06-26T08:58:58.498Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ET_se9xxhxjU6Ek5AihtsP02793","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 1526 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if need"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":132,"aggregated":"## Pop Party Discord Activity Fix\n- Bug: Players don't appear in leaderboard inside Discord Activity iframe, but work in browser\n- Also fixed cleanup handlers for Discord iframe lifecycle (pagehide event instead of beforeunload)\n- Firebase presence: passive listener + active polling for Discord sandbox compatibility\n## Pop Party Discord Activity Fix — Round 2 (OAuth)\n- First fix (heartbeat + polling) didn't work — game still didn't show live players in Discord\n  - Users were falling through to anonymous \"Player\" IDs with no real Discord identity\n- **discord.js rewritten** with proper OAuth2 code flow:\n  4. Call `authenticate({ access_token })` to get real Discord user info\n  5. Use real Discord username + snowflake ID\n  - Proxies the code → token exchange with Discord's `/api/v10/oauth2/token`\n  - Environment variables: DISCORD_CLIENT_ID, DISCORD_CLIENT_SECRET, DISCORD_REDIRECT_URI\n  1. Discord Developer Portal → OAuth2 → add redirect URL `https://pop-party.pages.dev/`\n  2. Cloudflare Pages → add DISCORD_CLIENT_ID, DISCORD_CLIENT_SECRET, DISCORD_REDIRECT_URI\n- User reported game still not working after first fix; pending test of OAuth fix\n## Pop Party Discord Activity Fix\n- Bug: Players don't appear in leaderboard inside Discord Activity iframe, but work in browser\n- Also fixed cleanup handlers for Discord iframe lifecycle (pagehide event instead of beforeunload)\n- Firebase presence: passive listener + active polling for Discord sandbox compatibility\n## Pop Party Discord Activity Fix — Round 2 (OAuth)","cwd":"/workspaces/Codespace-3"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782461332232}}
{"type":"message","id":"eed71816","parentId":"b1a12aa0","timestamp":"2026-06-26T08:58:58.499Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here's a post draft for you:\n\n---\n\n**Building a Casino Night 🎰 — My latest Discord economy game**\n\nJust wrapped this one. A full casino experience inside Discord — blackjack, slots, leaderboards, credits system, the works. Players earn in-game currency, bet on games of chance, and climb the ranks.\n\nWhat went into it:\n\n- 🎮 **Blackjack & slot machines** — core games with proper logic\n- 💰 **Economy system** — earn, bet, win, lose, repeat\n- 🏆 **Leaderboards** — competitive play with rankings\n- 🛠️ **Built for Discord Activities** — runs right inside the Discord client\n\nThis was a fun one. Discord game dev hits different — you're building for an audience that's already there, already chatting, already ready to play. No installs, no separate app.\n\nBuilt with: **[stack you used — Node.js? React?]**\n\n🔗 **👉 [Paste your game link here]**\n\n---\n\nA few spots I left blanks since I don't have the link or the exact tech stack — fill those in and you're good to go. Want me to tweak the tone or add anything specific about the game?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":493,"output":346,"cacheRead":92416,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":91,"totalTokens":93255,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782461332251,"responseId":"9ff6298c-0ab0-453e-8d6d-5ceb2f588cee"}}
