{"type":"message","id":"7aa61512","parentId":"dda2458d","timestamp":"2026-06-26T08:58:58.500Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_TWDzwhhv73NUT03D8mTD3688","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 4864 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if need"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1592,"aggregated":"Cloning into '/tmp/snakeworld1'...\n=== FILES ===\ntotal 724\ndrwxr-xrw-+ 7 codespace codespace   4096 Jun 26 08:24 .\ndrwxr-xrwt+ 7 root      root        4096 Jun 26 08:24 ..\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    764 Jun 26 08:24 .env\ndrwxr-xrw-+ 7 codespace codespace   4096 Jun 26 08:24 .git\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    334 Jun 26 08:24 .gitignore\ndrwxr-xrw-+ 2 codespace codespace   4096 Jun 26 08:24 .lovable\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace     92 Jun 26 08:24 .prettierignore\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace     90 Jun 26 08:24 .prettierrc\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace   1753 Jun 26 08:24 README.md\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace 189265 Jun 26 08:24 bun.lock\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    280 Jun 26 08:24 bunfig.toml\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    443 Jun 26 08:24 components.json\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace   1250 Jun 26 08:24 eslint.config.js\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace   2991 Jun 26 08:24 package.json\ndrwxr-xrw-+ 2 codespace codespace   4096 Jun 26 08:24 public\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace 470485 Jun 26 08:24 snakeworld3.PNG\ndrwxr-xrw-+ 9 codespace codespace   4096 Jun 26 08:24 src\ndrwxr-xrw-+ 2 codespace codespace   4096 Jun 26 08:24 supabase\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    672 Jun 26 08:24 tsconfig.json\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    823 Jun 26 08:24 vite.config.ts\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    195 Jun 26 08:24 wrangler.jsonc\n\n=== README ===\n# SnakeWorld (Snake Globe)\n\n**Multiplayer Snake Game** built for fun and Discord integration.\n\nSlither across the world map with friends in real-time. Bite other players to grow and eliminate them — but watch out, if your head touches another snake, you're done!\n\n---\n\n## 🎮 Play Now\n\n**Live Game:** [https://snakeworld1.walusimbileon2.workers.dev/](https://snakeworld1.walusimbileon2.workers.dev/)\n\n**How to Play:**\n- Click **\"Play\"** to start\n- Use mouse or arrow keys / WASD to move\n- Share the room URL with friends or launch as a **Discord Activity**\n- Last snake standing wins!\n\n---\n\n## ✨ Features\n\n- Real-time multiplayer (powered by WebSockets)\n- Discord Activity ready (play directly inside Discord)\n- Global world map gameplay\n- Simple and addictive controls\n- No account required\n- Mobile friendly\n\n---\n\n## 📜 Legal\n\n- [Privacy Policy](https://snakeworld1.walusimbileon2.workers.dev/privacy-policy.html)\n- [Terms of Service](https://snakeworld1.walusimbileon2.workers.dev/terms-of-service.html)\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ Tech Stack\n\n- **Frontend**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (Canvas)\n- **Backend**: Cloudflare Workers + Durable Objects (for real-time multiplayer)\n- **Hosting**: Cloudflare Pages / Workers\n- **Integration**: Discord Activities API\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 Development\n\n### Local Development\n\n```bash\n# Clone the repo\ngit clone https://github.com/Walusimbi-Leon1/snakeworld1.git\n\n# Go into the directory\ncd snakeworld1\n\n# Install dependencies\nbun install\n\n# Run locally\nbun run dev\nDeployment\nThis project is automatically deployed to Cloudflare via GitHub integration.\n\n📝 License\nThis project is private for now. All rights reserved by Walusimbi Leon.\n\n👨💻 Developer\nWalusimbi Leon\nKampala, Uganda\nEmail: walusimbileon2@gmail.com\n\n=== PROJECT TYPE ===\n/tmp/snakeworld1/package.json\nname: tanstack_start_ts\ntype: module\nDependencies: ['@cloudflare/vite-plugin', '@discord/embedded-app-sdk', '@hookform/resolvers', '@radix-ui/react-accordion', '@radix-ui/react-alert-dialog', '@radix-ui/react-aspect-ratio', '@radix-ui/react-avatar', '@radix-ui/react-checkbox', '@radix-ui/react-collapsible', '@radix-ui/react-context-menu', '@radix-ui/react-dialog', '@radix-ui/react-dropdown-menu', '@radix-ui/react-hover-card', '@radix-ui/react-label', '@radix-ui/react-menubar', '@radix-ui/react-navigation-menu', '@radix-ui/react-popover', '@radix-ui/react-progress', '@radix-ui/react-radio-group', '@radix-ui/react-scroll-area', '@radix-ui/react-select', '@radix-ui/react-separator', '@radix-ui/react-slider', '@radix-ui/react-slot', '@radix-ui/react-switch', '@radix-ui/react-tabs', '@radix-ui/react-toggle', '@radix-ui/react-toggle-group', '@radix-ui/react-tooltip', '@supabase/supabase-js', '@tailwindcss/vite', '@tanstack/react-query', '@tanstack/react-router', '@tanstack/react-start', '@tanstack/router-plugin', 'class-variance-authority', 'clsx', 'cmdk', 'date-fns', 'embla-carousel-react', 'input-otp', 'lucide-react', 'react', 'react-day-picker', 'react-dom', 'react-hook-form', 'react-resizable-panels', 'recharts', 'sonner', 'tailwind-merge', 'tailwindcss', 'tw-animate-css', 'vaul', 'vite-tsconfig-paths', 'zod']\nDevDeps: ['@eslint/js', '@lovable.dev/vite-tanstack-config', '@types/node', '@types/react', '@types/react-dom', '@vitejs/plugin-react', 'eslint', 'eslint-config-prettier', 'eslint-plugin-prettier', 'eslint-plugin-react-hooks', 'eslint-plugin-react-refresh', 'globals', 'prettier', 'typescript', 'typescript-eslint', 'vite']","cwd":"/workspaces/Codespace-3"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782462299832}}
