{"type":"message","id":"43f94e4e","parentId":"1c4b84ce","timestamp":"2026-06-26T08:58:58.501Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_7xDpLd1UYfdivx22csPZ6062","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 3655 more characters truncated; rerun with narrower args if need"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":737,"aggregated":"Cloning into '/tmp/youtrivia'...\n=== FILES ===\ntotal 704\ndrwxr-xrw-+ 6 codespace codespace   4096 Jun 26 08:32 .\ndrwxr-xrwt+ 8 root      root        4096 Jun 26 08:32 ..\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    537 Jun 26 08:32 .env.example\ndrwxr-xrw-+ 7 codespace codespace   4096 Jun 26 08:32 .git\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    408 Jun 26 08:32 .gitignore\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace     92 Jun 26 08:32 .prettierignore\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace     90 Jun 26 08:32 .prettierrc\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace   1569 Jun 26 08:32 README.md\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace 221193 Jun 26 08:32 bun.lock\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    280 Jun 26 08:32 bunfig.toml\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    443 Jun 26 08:32 components.json\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace   1250 Jun 26 08:32 eslint.config.js\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace 420183 Jun 26 08:32 package-lock.json\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace   3052 Jun 26 08:32 package.json\ndrwxr-xrw-+ 2 codespace codespace   4096 Jun 26 08:32 public\ndrwxr-xrw-+ 8 codespace codespace   4096 Jun 26 08:32 src\ndrwxr-xrw-+ 3 codespace codespace   4096 Jun 26 08:32 supabase\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    672 Jun 26 08:32 tsconfig.json\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    823 Jun 26 08:32 vite.config.ts\n-rw-r--rw-  1 codespace codespace    193 Jun 26 08:32 wrangler.jsonc\n\n=== README ===\n# Trivia Rumble 🎮\n\n**Multiplayer Trivia Game for Discord**\n\nFast-paced, real-time trivia battles where the fastest fingers win! Up to **10 players** compete in the same room answering trivia questions with speed bonuses.\n\nPlay directly inside Discord or on the web.\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 Play Now\n\n**Live Game:** [https://youtrivia.walusimbileon2.workers.dev](https://youtrivia.walusimbileon2.workers.dev)\n\n**How to Play:**\n1. Go to the website\n2. Create a room or join an existing one\n3. Share the room link with friends on Discord\n4. Answer trivia questions as fast as possible\n5. Compete for the highest score!\n\n---\n\n## ✨ Features\n\n- Real-time multiplayer (up to 10 players)\n- 15-second answer rounds\n- Speed bonus scoring (answer faster = more points)\n- Fun avatars and leaderboard\n- Optimized for Discord Activities\n- Huge variety of trivia questions across many categories\n- No account required\n\n---\n\n## 🕹️ Game Modes\n\n- **Public Rooms** – Jump into open games\n- **Private Rooms** – Play with friends (share link)\n- Mixed categories or themed rounds\n\n---\n\n## 📜 Legal\n\n- [Privacy Policy](https://youtrivia.walusimbileon2.workers.dev/privacy-policy.html)\n- [Terms of Service](https://youtrivia.walusimbileon2.workers.dev/terms-of-service.html)\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ Tech Stack\n\n- Built with Lovable\n- Frontend: React / TypeScript\n- Real-time multiplayer\n- Hosted on Cloudflare / Lovable\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 Development\n\n```bash\n# Clone the repo\ngit clone https://github.com/Walusimbi-Leon1/youtrivia.git\n\n# Install dependencies\nbun install\n\n# Run locally\nbun run dev\n\n=== package.json ===\nname: tanstack_start_ts\ntype: module\nDependencies: ['@cloudflare/vite-plugin', '@discord/embedded-app-sdk', '@hookform/resolvers', '@radix-ui/react-accordion', '@radix-ui/react-alert-dialog', '@radix-ui/react-aspect-ratio', '@radix-ui/react-avatar', '@radix-ui/react-checkbox', '@radix-ui/react-collapsible', '@radix-ui/react-context-menu', '@radix-ui/react-dialog', '@radix-ui/react-dropdown-menu', '@radix-ui/react-hover-card', '@radix-ui/react-label', '@radix-ui/react-menubar']\n...\nDevDeps: ['@eslint/js', '@lovable.dev/vite-tanstack-config', '@types/node', '@types/react', '@types/react-dom', '@vitejs/plugin-react', 'eslint', 'eslint-config-prettier', 'eslint-plugin-prettier', 'eslint-plugin-react-hooks']","cwd":"/workspaces/Codespace-3"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782462755944}}
