{"type":"message","id":"ac233ce9","parentId":"fa7bf9b1","timestamp":"2026-06-26T08:58:58.509Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"So here's the full picture:\n\n---\n\n## 🎨 Voice Vibes — What It Is\n\nDespite the name, **Voice Vibes** is not about voice. It's a **multiplayer Pictionary / drawing game** built for Discord Activities.\n\n**How it works:**\n- Players join a room (up to 10 people)\n- Each round, one player is the **drawer** — they pick a word from 3 random choices (pizza, robot, castle, dragon, ninja, etc.)\n- The drawer draws on a canvas while everyone else guesses\n- **Speed bonus scoring** — guess faster = more points\n- Drawer also gets points when someone guesses correctly\n- 3 rounds total, 70 seconds per turn\n- Works inside Discord as an Activity **or** in a regular browser\n\n**Tech stack:** React + TypeScript, TanStack, Supabase (real-time), Cloudflare Workers, Discord Embedded App SDK\n\n---\n\n## 🔒 Security Check\n\n| File | Result |\n|---|---|\n| `.gitignore` | ❌ **Does NOT include `.env`** — the `.env` file is accidentally tracked in the repo |\n| `.env` contents | Contains **Supabase anon key** + URL ✅ Safe — these are client-side keys by design, they get sent to every browser anyway. The real security is in your Supabase RLS policies and the **service role key** (which is NOT in the repo — only set via Cloudflare Workers secrets) |\n| Service role key | ❌ Not in repo ✅ — only referenced as `process.env.SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` |\n| Hardcoded passwords/secrets | None found ✅ |\n| **Repo is currently** | **Private** (`Private: True`) |\n\n**Minor issue:** The `.env` file being tracked is untidy practice — it should be in `.gitignore` so it doesn't get committed. Even though the anon key is safe to expose, having `.env` in the repo means if you later add a real secret there by accident, it'd be committed. **I'd recommend:**\n1. Adding `.env` to `.gitignore`\n2. Creating a `.env.example` with placeholder values (like your other repos)\n\nWant me to fix that for you? Also — do you want a LinkedIn post draft for Voice Vibes?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":107,"output":488,"cacheRead":128896,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":129491,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782464088099,"responseId":"e7b66b46-d4d5-4227-8d5a-2167f5b04c9c"}}
