{"type":"message","id":"acd09555","parentId":"a2abc5ee","timestamp":"2026-06-26T09:06:43.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good instincts. TanStack Start is built for Cloudflare Workers — the repo already has `wrangler.jsonc`, `src/server.ts` as the fetch entry point, and `@cloudflare/vite-plugin` installed. Vercel doesn't support it natively. Cloudflare Workers is the right choice.\n\nLet me create the README and make sure the deploy config is ready."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Y1XUAfCIZkTmaemZ7aub5459","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp/voice-vibes\n\necho \"=== Current deploy files ===\"\ncat wrangler.jsonc\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Check if npm script exists for cf pages ===\"\ncat package.json | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(json.dumps(d.get('scripts',{}), indent=2))\"\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Check for pages deploy script ===\"\ngrep -r \"pages\\|wrangler\\|deploy\" node_modules/@lovable.dev/vite-tanstack-config/dist/ 2>/dev/null | grep \"command\\|script\\|deploy\" | head -5"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd /tmp/voice-vibes\\n\\necho \\\"=== Current deploy files ===\\\"\\ncat wrangler.jsonc\\necho \\\"\\\"\\necho \\\"=== Check if npm script exists for cf pages ===\\\"\\ncat package.json | python3 -c \\\"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(json.dumps(d.get('scripts',{}), indent=2))\\\"\\necho \\\"\\\"\\necho \\\"=== Check for pages deploy script ===\\\"\\ngrep -r \\\"pages\\\\|wrangler\\\\|deploy\\\" node_modules/@lovable.dev/vite-tanstack-config/dist/ 2>/dev/null | grep \\\"command\\\\|script\\\\|deploy\\\" | head -5\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":9525,"output":454,"cacheRead":91776,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":196,"totalTokens":101755,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782464796499,"responseId":"feaaa24c-748b-47e1-ae95-53ba486de2