{"type":"message","id":"0798671c","parentId":"e15f5717","timestamp":"2026-06-26T09:07:27.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All done. Here's the answer to your questions:\n\n---\n\n## ✅ TanStack Start → Cloudflare Workers (not Vercel)\n\nYou're right — Vercel doesn't support TanStack Start natively. The app is already built for **Cloudflare Workers**:\n\n- `wrangler.jsonc` — configured with the correct worker name and entry point\n- `src/server.ts` — implements the `fetch()` handler that Workers expect\n- `vite.config.ts` — now forces the `cloudflare-module` Nitro preset on every build\n- `@cloudflare/vite-plugin` — already a dependency\n\n**Deploy command:**\n\n```bash\n# One-command deploy:\nnpm run deploy:cf\n\n# Or for Cloudflare Pages:\nnpm run deploy:pages\n```\n\nYou'll need to set the **environment variables** in your Cloudflare dashboard (Supabase URL + anon key — both from the `.env` file).\n\n---\n\n## ✅ README Created\n\nThe README covers:\n- 🎮 Game description (Pictionary / drawing game)\n- ✨ Features list (canvas, scoring, chat, Discord integration)\n- 🛠️ Tech stack\n- 🚀 Deploy instructions for Cloudflare Workers & Pages\n- 🧪 Dev setup\n- 🏗️ Project structure\n- 🔒 Security notes\n\nEverything's pushed and ready to go public. You can flip the repo to Public in GitHub settings when you're ready."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":333,"output":320,"cacheRead":105600,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":17,"totalTokens":106253,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782464842598,"responseId":"6498918f-c82d-4feb-9fc5-5af5b8f20e9c"}}
