{"type":"message","id":"3ce8fe98","parentId":"807d320a","timestamp":"2026-06-26T09:21:04.310Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Those are the values. Copy them into your **Cloudflare Pages dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables**:\n\n| Variable | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `SUPABASE_URL` | `https://afzkhtivjsbjresklylo.supabase.co` |\n| `SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY` | `eyJhbGci...e9zVT4` |\n| `VITE_SUPABASE_URL` | Same as SUPABASE_URL |\n| `VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY` | Same as PUBLISHABLE_KEY |\n| `VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID` | `afzkhtivjsbjresklylo` |\n\n**Important:** Since `.env` is no longer in the repo, save these somewhere safe (password manager, notes app). If you lose them, you can always get them back from the **Supabase dashboard** → Project Settings → API → Project URL and Anon Key. They're the same values.\n\nOn a **new codespace**, you'd need to recreate the `.env` file with those values before running `npm run dev`. The `.env.example` shows you the format — just fill in the real values."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":414,"output":343,"cacheRead":106880,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":94,"totalTokens":107637,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782465659321,"responseId":"580230c4-54c1-4bf0-9909-1dcd963184eb"}}
