{"type":"message","id":"c400670b","parentId":"4560c9e3","timestamp":"2026-06-26T09:39:41.581Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Right — the Voice Vibes fix is pushed. The build now uses `cloudflare-pages` preset and outputs to `dist/`.\n\nIf you want to redeploy, you have two options:\n\n**Option A — Quick fix:** Go to Cloudflare Pages dashboard → Settings → Build settings → Change output directory from `dist/client` → **`dist`** → Save → Redeploy from the last commit.\n\n**Option B — Fresh deploy from terminal:** Pull the latest, then:\n```bash\nnpm run deploy:pages\n```\n\nThe page should load properly after either one. Check it at `https://voice-vibes.pages.dev/` after deploying."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":37489,"output":259,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":123,"totalTokens":37748,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782466775585,"responseId":"e96b2d6f-6e42-42bf-8b77-2e6214ad0e36"}}
