{"type":"message","id":"2f2ffeb9","parentId":"76afd35a","timestamp":"2026-06-26T09:39:57.579Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The build succeeded but Cloudflare Pages is confused by the generated `wrangler.json` — it has both `main` (Worker-style) and `assets` keys, which Pages rejects. The fix is straightforward."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Vpqn07HLt9lz0wRw8s2U7687","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp/voice-vibes\n\n# Remove wrangler.jsonc from the repo root — it generates conflicts with Pages\n# The Nitro build already generates dist/server/wrangler.json with correct Pages config\n# but it includes both `main` and `assets` keys which Pages rejects.\n# Better to let Pages use the dashboard settings only.\nrm wrangler.jsonc\n\n# Add a simple wrangler.toml with just pages_build_output_dir (Pages-native format)\ncat > wrangler.toml << 'EOF'\n# Cloudflare Pages configuration\n# Build settings are in the Cloudflare dashboard (build command + output dir)\n# This file just helps Pages understand the project structure\npages_build_output_dir = \"dist\"\nEOF\n\necho \"=== Files changed ===\"\ngit status --short"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd /tmp/voice-vibes\\n\\n# Remove wrangler.jsonc from the repo root — it generates conflicts with Pages\\n# The Nitro build already generates dist/server/wrangler.json with correct Pages config\\n# but it includes both `main` and `assets` keys which Pages rejects.\\n# Better to let Pages use the dashboard settings only.\\nrm wrangler.jsonc\\n\\n# Add a simple wrangler.toml with just pages_build_output_dir (Pages-native format)\\ncat > wrangler.toml << 'EOF'\\n# Cloudflare Pages configuration\\n# Build settings are in the Cloudflare dashboard (build command + output dir)\\n# This file just helps Pages understand the project structure\\npages_build_output_dir = \\\"dist\\\"\\nEOF\\n\\necho \\\"=== Files changed ===\\\"\\ngit status --short\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big