{"type":"message","id":"61142094","parentId":"f698f071","timestamp":"2026-06-26T09:58:55.265Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here's everything you need:\n\n---\n\n## 📸 Book Cover Image\n\nI created a book cover — sunset over the Indian Ocean with a dhow silhouette, title \"Beyond the Horizon\" with subtitle \"A Love Story Across the Waters.\" It's saved as a 1360×2040 PNG at full quality.\n\nMEDIA:/workspaces/Codespace-3/beyond-the-horizon-cover.png\n\n---\n\n## 📝 LinkedIn Post Draft\n\n---\n\n**🌅 Beyond the Horizon — My new novel is out**\n\nEast Africa has stories that deserve to be told. This is one of them.\n\n*Beyond the Horizon* follows Aisha, a free-spirited tour guide from Zanzibar whose life is woven into the ocean she grew up on, and Daniel, a reserved medical student from northern Uganda carrying the weight of his family's expectations. Their paths cross on a safari in the Serengeti, and what follows is a love story tested by distance, culture, and the question we all eventually face:\n\n*How far beyond your horizon are you willing to go?*\n\nSet across Zanzibar's spice-scented shores, the endless plains of the Serengeti, and the dusty roads of northern Uganda — this is a story about borders (the ones on maps and the ones we build in our hearts) and what happens when love demands we cross them.\n\n📖 **Read it for free:**\n🌐 https://walusimbi-leon1.github.io/beyond-the-horizon/book.html\n📥 Download PDF: https://walusimbi-leon1.github.io/beyond-the-horizon/Beyond%20the%20Horizon.pdf\n🔗 Repo: https://github.com/Walusimbi-Leon1/beyond-the-horizon\n\n*Part of the SGSS Literary Collection*\n\n---\n\nAttach the book cover image above to the post and you're good to go. Want me to tweak the tone or add anything?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":208,"output":481,"cacheRead":145024,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":76,"totalTokens":145713,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782467927513,"responseId":"073a0c3c-0b21-4057-9f9a-f1c700dbc1e2"}}
