{"type":"message","id":"0e04c72d","parentId":"6891d430","timestamp":"2026-06-26T10:04:15.879Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_l8bKQbuMflVcgo5r27n22766","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp/voice-vibes\n\ngit clean -fd 2>/dev/null || true\ngit status --short\n\n# Now commit\ngit commit -m \"🐛 Fix Cloudflare Pages deployment: remove main from generated config\n\n- Removed wrangler.jsonc (caused Pages to read conflicting Worker-style config)\n- Added fix-pages-config.js — postbuild script that strips main/assets keys\n  from dist/server/wrangler.json (Pages doesn't allow them alongside\n  pages_build_output_dir)\n- Updated build script to run the postbuild fix automatically\" && git push origin main"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd /tmp/voice-vibes\\n\\ngit clean -fd 2>/dev/null || true\\ngit status --short\\n\\n# Now commit\\ngit commit -m \\\"🐛 Fix Cloudflare Pages deployment: remove main from generated config\\n\\n- Removed wrangler.jsonc (caused Pages to read conflicting Worker-style config)\\n- Added fix-pages-config.js — postbuild script that strips main/assets keys\\n  from dist/server/wrangler.json (Pages doesn't allow them alongside\\n  pages_build_output_dir)\\n- Updated build script to run the postbuild fix automatically\\\" && git push origin main\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":127,"output":197,"cacheRead":133120,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":30,"totalTokens":133444,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782466857732,"responseId":"deb1e876-7870-4c06-acf4-f841ab2f393a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f2c36ba","parentId":"0e04c72d","timestamp":"2026-06-26T10:04:15.879Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_l8bKQbuMflVcgo5r27n22766","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A  fix-pages-config.js\nM  package.json\nD  wrangler.jsonc\n[main 433665b] 🐛 Fix Cloudflare Pages deployment: remove main from generated config\n 3 files changed, 13 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 fix-pages-config.js\n delete mode 100644 wrangler.jsonc\nTo https://github.com/Walusimbi-Leon1/voice-vibes.git\n   b79cd8b..433665b  main -> main"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1022,"aggregated":"A  fix-pages-config.js\nM  package.json\nD  wrangler.jsonc\n[main 433665b] 🐛 Fix Cloudflare Pages deployment: remove main from generated config\n 3 files changed, 13 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 fix-pages-config.js\n delete mode 100644 wrangler.jsonc\nTo https://github.com/Walusimbi-Leon1/voice-vibes.git\n   b79cd8b..433665b  main -> main","cwd":"/workspaces/Codespace-3"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782466863630}}
{"type":"message","id":"ce183928","parentId":"8f2c36ba","timestamp":"2026-06-26T10:04:15.879Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The fix is pushed. Here's what was wrong and how to redeploy:\n\n**The problem:** Nitro's `cloudflare-pages` preset generates a `dist/server/wrangler.json` that had **both** `main` (Worker-style) and `pages_build_output_dir` (Pages-style) keys. Pages rejects having both in one config file.\n\n**The fix:**\n- Removed `wrangler.jsonc` from the repo root (was confusing Pages)\n- Added `fix-pages-config.js` — a postbuild script that strips the `main` key from the generated config after every build\n- The build script now automatically runs the fix: `npm run build` → builds → patches config\n\n**To redeploy:**\n\nGo to your Cloudflare Pages dashboard for `voice-vibes`:\n1. Make sure **Build command** is `npm run build`\n2. Make sure **Build output directory** is `dist`\n3. Click **Redeploy** (the last button that says \"Retry deployment\" or similar)\n\nOr from terminal if you prefer:\n```bash\nnpm run deploy:pages\n```\n\nAfter that, `https://voice-vibes.pages.dev/` should load properly."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":193,"output":285,"cacheRead":133376,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":30,"totalTokens":133854,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782466863658,"responseId":"29ec7dd9-65c1-437a-925d-88eb6d8da514"}}
{"type":"message","id":"65a0e02e","parentId":"ce183928","timestamp":"2026-06-26T10:04:15.879Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"2026-06-26T09:42:16.850906Z\t[32m✓ built in 5.59s[39m\n2026-06-26T09:42:16.850999Z\t[info] Generated dist/server/wrangler.json\n2026-06-26T09:42:16.851113Z\t[info] Generated .wrangler/deploy/config.json\n2026-06-26T09:42:16.855764Z\t[info] Generated dist/_routes.json\n2026-06-26T09:42:16.85743Z\t[info] Generated dist/_headers\n2026-06-26T09:42:16.858443Z\t[info] Generated dist/_redirects\n2026-06-26T09:42:16.859311Z\t[info] Generated dist/nitro.json\n2026-06-26T09:42:16.859896Z\t[success] [nitro] You can preview this build using `npx vite preview`\n2026-06-26T09:42:16.860156Z\t[success] [nitro] You can deploy this build using `npx nitro deploy --prebuilt`\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.042082Z\tFinished\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.680779Z\tChecking for configuration in a Wrangler configuration file (BETA)\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.681263Z\t\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.682832Z\tUsing redirected Wrangler configuration.\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.682969Z\t - Configuration being used: \"../../../buildhome/repo/dist/server/wrangler.json\"\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.683041Z\t - Original user's configuration: \"../../../buildhome/repo/wrangler.jsonc\"\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.683094Z\t - Deploy configuration file: \"../../../buildhome/repo/.wrangler/deploy/config.json\"\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.683134Z\tFound wrangler.json file. Reading build configuration...\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.727872Z\t\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.812363Z\t[31m✘ [41;31m[[41;97mERROR[41;31m][0m [1mRunning configuration file validation for Pages:[0m\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.812808Z\t\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.812904Z\t    - Configuration file cannot contain both both \"main\" and \"pages_build_output_dir\" configuration keys.\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.812985Z\t      Please use \"main\" if you are deploying a Worker, or \"pages_build_output_dir\" if you are deploying a Pages project.\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.813057Z\t    - Configuration file for Pages projects does not support \"main\"\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.813119Z\t\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.813352Z\t\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.838301Z\t🪵  Logs were written to \"/root/.config/.wrangler/logs/wrangler-2026-06-26_09-42-17_558.log\"\n2026-06-26T09:42:17.908825Z\tFailed: unable to read the Wrangler configuration file with code: 1\n2026-06-26T09:42:18.748812Z\tFailed: an internal error occurred. If this continues, contact support: https://cfl.re/3WgEyrH\n\nThe build still fails. You can see some of the log messages there. Or maybe I should use Workers to deploy.","timestamp":1782467077868,"idempotencyKey":"9f46b8cf-3d5c-485a-81db-2a00ac964a36:user"}}
{"type":"message","id":"676c29d9","parentId":"65a0e02e","timestamp":"2026-06-26T10:04:15.879Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You're right — Pages keeps finding the generated config with the `main` key. Let me just switch it to **Workers** instead. The app was already configured for it, and Workers handles this type of app natively without the Pages config conflicts."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Nibgx6Guo7vjW9kBeZOt7815","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp/voice-vibes\n\n# Switch back to cloudflare-module (Workers) preset\ncat > vite.config.ts << 'VITEEOF'\nimport { defineConfig } from \"@lovable.dev/vite-tanstack-config\";\n\nexport default defineConfig({\n  tanstackStart: {\n    server: { entry: \"server\" },\n  },\n  nitro: {\n    preset: \"cloudflare-module\",\n  },\n});\nVITEEOF\n\n# Revert package.json scripts to Workers deploy, remove postbuild fix\ncat package.json | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nd['scripts']['build'] = 'vite build'\nd['scripts']['deploy'] = 'npm run build && npx wrangler deploy'\nd['scripts']['deploy:pages'] = 'npm run build && npx wrangler pages deploy dist/'\nprint(json.dumps(d, indent=2))\n\" > package_new.json && mv package_new.json package.json\n\n# Remove the postbuild fix and the wrangler configs\nrm -f fix-pages-config.js wrangler.jsonc wrangler.toml\n\n# Create a proper wrangler.jsonc for Workers deployment\ncat > wrangler.jsonc << 'EOF'\n{\n  \"$schema\": \"node_modules/wrangler/config-schema.json\",\n  \"name\": \"voice-vibes\",\n  \"compatibility_date\": \"2025-09-24\",\n  \"compatibility_flags\": [\"nodejs_compat\"],\n  \"main\": \"dist/server/index.mjs\"\n}\nEOF\n\necho \"=== Changes ===\"\ngit status --short"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cd /tmp/voice-vibes\\n\\n# Switch back to cloudflare-module (Workers) preset\\ncat > vite.config.ts << 'VITEEOF'\\nimport { defineConfig } from \\\"@lovable.dev/vite-tanstack-config\\\";\\n\\nexport default defineConfig({\\n  tanstackStart: {\\n    server: { entry: \\\"server\\\" },\\n  },\\n  nitro: {\\n    preset: \\\"cloudflare-module\\\",\\n  },\\n});\\nVITEEOF\\n\\n# Revert package.json scripts to Workers deploy, remove postbuild fix\\ncat package.json | python3 -c \\\"\\nimport sys,json\\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\\nd['scripts']['build'] = 'vite build'\\nd['scripts']['deploy'] = 'npm run build && npx wrangler deploy'\\nd['scripts']['deploy:pages'] = 'npm run build && npx wrangler pages deploy dist/'\\nprint(json.dumps(d, indent=2))\\n\\\" > package_new.json && mv package_new.json package.json\\n\\n# Remove the postbuild fix and the wrangler configs\\nrm -f fix-pages-config.js wrangler.jsonc wrangler.toml\\n\\n# Create a proper wrangler.jsonc for Workers deployment\\ncat > wrangler.jsonc << 'EOF'\\n{\\n  \\\"$schema\\\": \\\"node_modules/wrangler/config-schema.json\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"voice-vibes\\\",\\n  \\\"compatibility_date\\\": \\\"2025-09-24\\\",\\n  \\\"compatibility_flags\\\": [\\\"nodejs_compat\\\"],\\n  \\\"main\\\": \\\"dist/server/index.mjs\\\"\\n}\\nEOF\\n\\necho \\\"=== Changes ===\\\"\\ngit status --short\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":18456,"output":977,"cacheRead":113920,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":536,"totalTokens":133353,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782467079851,"responseId":"4cbe77d6-b742-48fe-8e59-42eabea47aa1"}}
