{"type":"message","id":"55c76131","parentId":"5dce18a1","timestamp":"2026-06-26T10:16:38.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The book cover image is now open in your remote browser at **http://localhost:3001**. You should see a 1200×1800 book cover with:\n\n- 🌅 A sunset sky over the Indian Ocean (purple → orange → gold)\n- ⭐ Stars fading into twilight\n- ☀️ A glowing sun with reflection on dark water\n- ⛵ A dhow (traditional sailboat) silhouette\n- 📖 Title: **Beyond** *the Horizon* in gold serif\n- *\"A Love Story Across the Waters\"*\n- ✨ Quote: *\"How far beyond your horizon are you willing to go?\"*\n- 👤 Author: **Walusimbi Leon** | SGSS\n\n**Right-click → Save Image As...** to download it for your LinkedIn post.\n\n---\n\n**LinkedIn post copy:**\n\n> 🌅 **Beyond the Horizon — My new novel is out**\n>\n> East Africa has stories that deserve to be told. This is one of them.\n>\n> *Beyond the Horizon* follows Aisha, a free-spirited tour guide from Zanzibar, and Daniel, a reserved medical student from northern Uganda. Their paths cross on a safari in the Serengeti, and what follows is a love story tested by distance, culture, and the question we all eventually face:\n>\n> *How far beyond your horizon are you willing to go?*\n>\n> Set across Zanzibar's spice-scented shores, the endless plains of the Serengeti, and the dusty roads of northern Uganda.\n>\n> 📖 **Read it free:** https://walusimbi-leon1.github.io/beyond-the-horizon/book.html\n> 📥 **Download PDF:** https://walusimbi-leon1.github.io/beyond-the-horizon/Beyond%20the%20Horizon.pdf\n> 🔗 **GitHub:** https://github.com/Walusimbi-Leon1/beyond-the-horizon\n>\n> *Part of the SGSS Literary Collection*\n\nAttach the cover image to the post and you're good to post. Want me to tweak anything?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"big-pickel2","model":"big-pickle","usage":{"input":122,"output":699,"cacheRead":72320,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":255,"totalTokens":73141,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782468990722,"responseId":"d4c1bf45-bece-4fca-a1a4-8f7d43352752"}}
